dct_title_s: Map of the state of South Dakota
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading.; Shows township and range, counties, towns, railroads, water features, and areas containing coal. Also shows Indian, military and forest reservations.; Prime meridians: Greenwich (top) and Washington, D.C. (bottom).; At head of title: Department of the Interior, General Land Office, Hon. Binger Hermann, Commissioner.; Dec. 19 1906 and S Doc 194 59 2-- lower right margin.
